{"tid":1962154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★馬莎多3人　發病後有返工做銷售收銀","createTime":"2020-04-07T09:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T09:47:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cec9c13b8b13aefc2ae425b6509132e9cebc62d1","tid":1962154,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"#923、#925、#932，與#903銅鑼灣CEO Neway唱K群組有關，四人均是馬莎不同地方工作的員工，相信在當日唱K受感染。記者問瑪莎仍營業是否恰當，張竹君指相信在唱K時感染。有個別知道幾時最後幾時返工，有些是發病後又返工，做銷售或收銀，有戴口罩，擔心一同食飯同事是密切接觸。三人有去不同分店，初步知道#923尖沙咀、#925銅鑼灣、#932在上環及灣仔分店。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/457668/新冠肺炎-直播-增21確診-馬莎多3人-發病後有返工做銷售收銀\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F457668%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E5%A2%9E21%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E9%A6%AC%E8%8E%8E%E5%A4%9A3%E4%BA%BA-%E7%99%BC%E7%97%85%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5%E5%81%9A%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E6%94%B6%E9%8A%80&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=36106f5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/457668/新冠肺炎-直播-增21確診-馬莎多3人-發病後有返工做銷售收銀</a>"},{"pid":"97f061fbda0c90279c62fe327c6562ea13a65921","tid":1962154,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeedd19724a9ae06b52ad62e2692a7879bcdb1af","tid":1962154,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"點解仲可以繼續營業 <br />\n<br />\n同佢一齊番工啲同事唔洗隔